title: Week 17 Preview 2021
description:
Field Yates, Mike Clay, Stephania Bell and Daniel Dopp talk the latest injury updates, the WR/CB matchups to watch for the week and what players you can trust still in the fantasy playoffs. Plus, we pay tribute to two fantastic members of the football community.
